metadata.description: Bored.Ai Collective Text2Art #1, The Bored.Ai Collective is a creative community that grants its members access to the Bored.Ai suite of tools and technologies as they roll out over time and space. Bored.Ai Collective members get exclusive access to use the artificial intelligence, members-only spaces and perks, and NFT drops. Visit https://bored.ai for more information.
